Syntax: target <victim>

Marks a specific opponent as your priority target and immediately strikes
them. Target is a precision skill that forces a single decisive hit on the
named character. If you are currently fighting a different opponent, you
will disengage and redirect your attack.

Requirements:
  - Must have the Target skill at 65% proficiency or higher.
  - The target must be in the same room.
  - Cannot target innocent PCs (players without PKill/Thief flags) unless
    you are in a deathmatch.
  - Cannot target charmed creatures outside of a deathmatch.

Effects:
  - Executes one_hit() on the named target.
  - If you were fighting someone else, combat is re-targeted.
  - Sets a 1-pulse wait state after use.

See also: shelp target kill assist
